{
  "stem": "12462.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to make a speech and have all my six deputies across the country make little talks about what we'd been doing, and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After that was over, I-- well, in the process of doing that, I got to know a tremendous number of professors who were in the field of behavioral science.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of them, Gordon Lippitt, Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gordon Lippitt, suggested that we form a group and use these people in order to run training programs and to charge industry people and other voluntary organizations for training.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that we would conduct these five-day or six-day workshops in which we exposed them to a lot of things that they had missed in their adult education.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these turned out to be very successful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In this firm, we had leadership resources-- continued on for some time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, I moved from being executive director to being president of the leadership resources.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, as I say, we had-- I'd inherited a little money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we invested it in land out in the country, in Montgomery County.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that took some time, as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maryland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] I met my wife, Virginia, about six months before I left Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was on a tour, [CLEARS THROAT] with a group of Wellesley students and friends of hers, of Europe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Russell, the Secretary General of the tribunals, had asked her to come to visit him, just to see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she came to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was introduced to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this started a little correspondence by mail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came back to the States, I pursued her further.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And eventually, we got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In September-- [HOLDS HAND TO EAR AS IF LISTENING]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1949.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1949.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
